    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It runs super smoothly and is ready for its next big adventure! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014I think you're going to love how it handles!",
