      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L straight-six. This unit features a reinforced rear subframe and a recently serviced VANOS system, addressing the platform's primary structural and timing concerns. The 6-speed manual transmission shifts with precision, delivering torque through a functional M-Variable differential. The suspension geometry remains true, benefiting from updated control arm bushings and dampers. Valvetrain clearances have been shimmed to spec, ensuring the individual throttle bodies provide the signature induction note and linear throttle response this chassis is renowned for. A focused example for the purist prioritizing drivetrain health and kinetic performance.",
